Cc: linux-snps-arc@lists.infradead.org
Cc: <stable@vger.kernel.org> # 4.4+
Signed-off-by: Ulf Hansson <ulf.hansson@linaro.org>
Signed-off-by: Greg Kroah-Hartman <gregkh@linuxfoundation.org>
